INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2017-05-11 12:51:32','2017-05-11 12:51:32','<ol>\r\n 	<li><strong>Graffiti:</strong> Color is a potent element of visual communication, we need to think through how and why we are using it. The way we use different colors has a dramatic impact on how we subconsciously relate to objects. Our Sector 51 Pathshala received a new avatar from Ms. Shikha , Ms. Reena and the volunteers of the team \"Udaan Ek Metha Sapna\" where graffiti were painted on all the walls of the pathshala. The walls were decorated with the pictures of animals portraying different stories and with kids holding out numbers and alphabets. Even the outer walls of the garden were painted with the figures of education. The walls typically spoke of allegories through images. Colors in kids\' surroundings help boost activity, orange has shown to increase performance, yellow increases emotion of joy, blue helps create a state of relaxation and calmness. A creative environment leads to creative minds.<strong>\r\n</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[video width=\"400\" height=\"224\" mp4=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/18998465_297875697320168_6425362295626399744_n.mp4\"][/video]\r\n\r\nStarted Today 3rd Freepathshala in Gurgaon.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wrap align-right\" src=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18527702_1418505301543536_6298244914611962087_n.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1001\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wrap align-right\" src=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18664365_1418505331543533_3905917840798252670_n.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1001\" />\r\n\r\nThis is 2nd Freepathshala in sector 46.\r\n1. Sadbhawna Park, near Amity Global ,Sec 46\r\n2. Sirchotu Ram Park near Jain Hospital Sec46\r\n\r\nConstruction workers need it at every Km.\r\n#iamgurgaon','Education','','publish','open','open','','education','','','2017-07-06 12:07:55','2017-07-06 12:07:55','',0,'http://t12pathshala.co.nf/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2017-05-11 12:51:32','2017-05-11 12:51:32','<b>Freepathshala</b> has done some successful events in the field of education for the needy children\'s and also freepathshala is taking some initiative to support the quote <b>\"ONE PATHSHALA PER KILOMETER\"</b> \r\nSome of the Freepathshala events and Initiatives are:-\r\n\r\n<b>1) Girl Child and Women Empowerment:</b> Activities and Events related to girl child development and spreading awareness about women rights.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wrap align-right\" src=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18556379_1418402888220444_4424697214686493849_n.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1001\" />\r\n\r\n<b>2) Specially Challenged Kids:</b> Activities and events related to providing benefits to special kids.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wrap align-right\" src=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/child.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1001\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>3) Health Care:</b> Activities and events related to food supplements and other health care initiatives like eye check-up and health check-up camps.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wrap align-right\" src=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/14441085_1186200824773986_2319920063021912168_n.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1001\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>4) Education:</b> The activities and events related to educational benefits in every Freepathshala.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wrap align-right\" src=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/14720624_1198905393503529_3894933365093853169_n.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1001\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>5) Workshops:</b> Description about various workshops organized in association with other firms or organizations.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wrap align-right\" src=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/15135748_1230006973726704_6251815086089358070_n.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1001\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n','Events And Initiative','','publish','closed','open','','events','','','2017-06-02 11:06:02','2017-06-02 11