ons whenever required, to push their minds to ponder over other ways to solve a problem. The roadmap would help the kids think of other possible ways of reaching the pathshala if any one of the route is blocked due to some reason. It may also help them guide people to either the pathshala or their houses. If a situation arises that the kid is lost in the city, the design would help him identify the possible routes to reach his destination. The activity was performed in the month of march in HUDA park. The students counted trees in the region by drawing circles and also drafted a pathway from the park with the elements that they usually spot on the way. The task is our step to provide the kids with an out of the box thinking capability and for the comprehensive development of the kids.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-658\" src=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/unnamed.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"884\" height=\"662\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-660\" src=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/17361630_1649160552045760_7311229945647874152_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"348\" height=\"463\" /> <img class=\" wp-image-661 alignnone\" src=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/17362431_1649160612045754_5807452170966717960_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"343\" height=\"456\" />','Up-Skilling','This is the excerpt for a featured post.','inherit','closed','closed','','154-revision-v1','','','2017-06-27 15:08:55','2017-06-27 15:08:55','',154,'http://t12pathshala.co.nf/2017/06/154-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(403,1,'2017-05-28 05:12:36','2017-05-28 05:12:36','<b><i>And Suddenly You Know....\nIts Time To Start Something New And Trust The Magic Of New Beginnings ... </i></b>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">-Miester Ackhart, Author</p>\nThe organization traces its mild beginnings from one of the usual warm summer dawns of June 2015, when Roshan Kumar Rawat, the founder-cum-heart-and-soul of our organization offered one of the labor to develop his child; to impart the gift of education which is still not written in the destiny of many lives.\nMr. Rawat, the usual Morning person, had never thought that one day his mornings may conjure up a miracle called FREEPATHSHALA.\nSlowly, the beginning time of 0800 hours was bring forward to 0730 hours, with further shifting to 0700 hours, making its genesis at 0600 hours with the Sun. A single kid changed to group of 5, then a dozen in no time, and furthermore 20 by the following June when Mr. Rawats parking lot gave way to the Society Mandir. During the succeeding months, it got replaced by a full fledged classroom. And today, we stand strong in this cause made to survive the millenniums to come, spreading the light of education on this community.','Our Inception','','inherit','closed','closed','','206-autosave-v1','','','2017-05-28 05:12:36','2017-05-28 05:12:36','',206,'http://t12pathshala.co.nf/2017/05/206-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(405,1,'2017-05-28 05:14:33','2017-05-28 05:14:33','<b><i>No Matter How Long Your Journey Appears To Be, There Is Never More Than This :One Step, One Breath , One Moment-now</i></b>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><b><i>-</i></b> Eckhart Tolle, Author</p>\nEmerging out of a parking lot, weve come a long way to accomplish a FREEPATHSHALA every kilometer. We have struggled, endured, shared, laughed and loved all the moments together.\nAfter the summer of first year, it was exhilarating to see volunteers and students both stacking up but we are all aware of a crest being always accompanied by a trough. When winters came, there was a dearth of volunteers, getting tangled up with their own lives.\nThere were hard times when people backed off after being hired. After all not everyone is strong enough to dive into this pile of mud and make a garden out of it.\nBut still, as they say <i>kisi cheez ko sachhe dil se pane ki koshish kro toh sari kaynat tumhe usse milane me lag jati hai</i>, we are here against all odds, fighting together for a better tomorrow.','Our Journey','','inherit','closed','closed','','6-autosave-v1','','','2017-05-28 05:14:33','2017-05-28 05:14:33','',6,'http://t12pathshala.co.nf/2017/05/6-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(410,1,'2017-05-28 07:44:32','2017-05-28 07:44:32','<center style=\"color: #008000;\">A FREEPATHSHALA PER KILOMETER!!</center>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<center><iframe style=\"border: 0;\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3508.5756214389226!2d77.06477411505907!3d28.432059499876672!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x390d1884886f654b%3A0x78fffa8dcd308f5c!2sPrinceton+Floors!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1495629681842\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></center><center><b>Address: First Park near Housing board colony,Sector 51,Gurgaon.</b></center>&nbsp;\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<center><iframe style=\"border: 0;\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3508.695789829721!2d77.056474715059!3d28.42843480003967!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x390d1880e593af1f%3A0xbe8311f3c44a0a01!2sJain+Hospital!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1495630487013\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></center><center><b>Addres: Sirchotu Ram Park near Jain Hospital, Sec46, Gurgaon.</b></center>&nbsp;\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<center><iframe style=\"border: 0;\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3508.4237357183133!2d77.06255081505917!3d28.436640299670675!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x390d18858763a543%3A0xac5dcf83e3ddad40!2sAmity+Global+School!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1495631075463\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></center><center><b>Address: Sadbhawna Park, near Amity Global ,Sec 46,Gurgaon.</b></center>','school locations','','inherit','closed','closed','','121-revision-v1','','','2017-05-28 