,'','2017-06-02 09:50:32','2017-06-02 09:50:32','',150,'http://t12pathshala.co.nf/2017/06/150-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(676,1,'2017-07-03 07:38:39','2017-07-03 07:38:39','Taking care of the Health of the children\'s is one of the prior concern of the Freepathshala. And taking mind in that we do have lots of activities and check-ups of the children\'s .\r\n\r\nFollowing are some steps in the Health section is :-\r\n\r\n1) <b> EYE CHECK-UPS:-</b> Freepathshala has done eye check up for the children after every four months with proper machinery and medicines from the eye specialized doctor.\r\n\r\n \r\n<img class=\"wrap align-right\" src=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/14441085_1186200824773986_2319920063021912168_n.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1001\" />\r\n\r\n2) <b> YOGA:- </b> Regular exercise and morning exercise with the yoga instructor to maintain harmony and peace in the mind plus make them physically strong.\r\n\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wrap align-right\" src=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/14639628_1223130211081047_1549998528076974194_n.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1001\" />\r\n\r\n3)<b>Good Touch and Bad Touch:-</b> In todays times, we hear a lot about child abuse and molestation. Each one of us want our children to be safe and secure and to protect them against all odds that come their way. As kids grow up, they start meeting new people they don\'t know and fall prey to immoral minds. Most of the time, targets are very young children, below 6-7 years of age. They are too young to understand the difference between right and wrong. Its high time, we start teaching young children about Good Touch Bad Touch to help prevent more damage. In association with the team of Hope Initiative, we decided to expound our kids about this topic. The kids were taught how to know if some person can cause them harm or already mistreats them and the measures that they could take in case they though that the person can cause them harm. Since their parents leave the house early in the morning to reach the construction site, there are many times the kids are left alone at home. Which is the time when we think the kids are the most susceptible to damage. This becomes our responsibility to equip and sensitise them to face any situation or person before the harm is done. We must all try to ensure that every kid becomes physically and emotionally strong to face every situation that must come their way.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wrap align-right\" src=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/16266221_1302941039766630_7458161962520732968_n.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1001\" />\r\n','Health','This is the excerpt for your very first post.','inherit','closed','closed','','5-revision-v1','','','2017-07-03 07:38:39','2017-07-03 07:38:39','',5,'http://t12pathshala.co.nf/2017/07/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(524,1,'2017-06-02 09:57:48','2017-06-02 09:57:48','/*\nYou can add your own CSS here.\n\nClick the help icon above to learn more.\n*/\na:link {\n    text-decoration: none;\n}\n\na:visited {\n    text-decoration: none;\n}\n','karuna-wpcom','','publish','closed','closed','','karuna-wpcom','','','2017-06-02 09:57:48','2017-06-02 09:57:48','',0,'http://t12pathshala.co.nf/2017/06/karuna-wpcom/',0,'custom_css','',0),(525,1,'2017-06-02 09:57:48','2017-06-02 09:57:48','/*\nYou can add your own CSS here.\n\nClick the help icon above to learn more.\n*/\na:link {\n    text-decoration: none;\n}\n\na:visited {\n    text-decoration: none;\n}\n','karuna-wpcom','','inherit','closed','closed','','524-revision-v1','','','2017-06-02 09:57:48','2017-06-02 09:57:48','',524,'http://t12pathshala.co.nf/2017/06/524-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(526,1,'2017-06-02 09:58:47','2017-06-02 09:58:47','&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong>Freepathshala is an initiative to educate children of construction workers.</strong></p>\r\n<b>FREEPATHSHALA HEADOFFICE:</b>\r\nADDRESS: FLAT NO.555 FF, HOUSING 