he most neglected class of our society  Migrant Workers. With the realization of CHANGE being the only constant in their lives, we help them to bring steadiness in their day to day undulations by providing their kids with education along with health concerns. Also, we encourage our little minds to actively participate in extracurricular activities with the view of their overall development.<br></P>\r\n      \r\n      <br>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n      <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-signal logo\"></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid bg-grey\">\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n      <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-globe logo slideanim\"></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n      \r\n      <h4><strong>MISSION AND VISION:<br><br><br>\r\n      Our mission At FREEPATHSHALA, we envision an India where every child of a nations builder is blessed with the invaluable education.</h4>\r\nOur mission is to envisage a FREEPATHSHALA in the vicinity of every kilometer of the nation.\r\n\r\nWe anticipate ourselves chasing our dreams at the velocity of<br><br>\r\nONE FREEPATHSHALA PER KILOMETER.</strong> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid bg-grey\">\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n      <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-flag logo slideanim\"></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n   \r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n      \r\n      <h4><strong>EVENTS AND INITIATIVES<br><br><br>\r\n      </strong> </p>\r\n       Freepathshala has done some successful events and take some of the great initiatives in the field of the education of the children\'s of the migrant workers.\r\n\r\nSome of the Events and Initiatives are:- \r\n<a href=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/events/\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Know More</button></a>\r\n\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n</htm