bring steadiness in their day to day undulations by providing their kids with education along with health concerns. Also, we encourage our little minds to actively participate in extracurricular activities with the view of their overall development.<br></P>\r\n      \r\n      <br>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n      <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-signal logo\"></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid bg-grey\">\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n      <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-globe logo slideanim\"></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n      \r\n      <h4><strong>MISSION AND VISION:<br><br><br>\r\n      Our mission At FREEPATHSHALA, we envision an India where every child of a nations builder is blessed with the invaluable education.</h4>\r\nOur mission is to envisage a FREEPATHSHALA in the vicinity of every kilometer of the nation.\r\n\r\nWe anticipate ourselves chasing our dreams at the velocity of<br><br>\r\nONE FREEPATHSHALA PER KILOMETER.</strong> </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid bg-grey\">\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n      <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-flag logo slideanim\"></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n   \r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n      \r\n      <h4><strong>EVENTS AND INITIATIVES<br><br><br>\r\n      </strong> </p>\r\n       Freepathshala has done some successful events and take some of the great initiatives in the field of the education of the children\'s of the migrant workers.\r\n\r\nSome of the Events and Initiatives are:- \r\n<a href=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/events/\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Know More</button></a>\r\n\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n \r\n\r\n','','','inherit','closed','closed','','150-revision-v1','','','2017-07-04 09:31:30','2017-07-04 09:31:30','',150,'http://t12pathshala.co.nf/2017/07/150-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(683,1,'2017-07-06 11:17:44','2017-07-06 11:17:44','<ol>\r\n 	<li><strong>Graffiti:</strong> Color is a potent element of visual communication, we need to think through how and why we are using it. The way we use different colors has a dramatic impact on how we subconsciously relate to objects. Our Sector 51 Pathshala recieved a new avtar from Ms. Shikha , Ms. Reena and the volunteers of the team \"Udaan Ek Metha Sapna\" where graffiti were painted on all the walls of the pathshala. The walls were decorated with the pictures of animals potraying different stories and with kids holding out numbers and alphabets. Even the outer walls of the garden were painted with the figures of education. The walls typically spoke of allogories through images. Colors in kids\' surroundings help boost activity, orange has shown to increase performance, yellow increases emotion of joy, blue helps create a state of relaxation and calmness. A creative environment leads to creative minds.<strong>\r\n</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nStarted Today 3rd Freepathshala in Gurgaon.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wrap align-right\" src=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18527702_1418505301543536_6298244914611962087_n.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1001\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wrap align-right\" src=\"http://t12pathshala.co.nf/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18664365_1418505331543533_3905917840798252670_n.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1001\" />\r\n\r\nThis is 2nd Freepathshala in sector 46.\r\n1. Sadbhawna Park, near Amity Global ,Sec 46\r\n2. Sirchotu Ram Park near Jain Hospital Sec46\r\n\r\nConstruction workers need it at every Km.\r\n#iamgurgaon','Education','','inherit','closed','closed','','1-revision-v1','','','2017-07-06 11:17:44','2017-07-06 11:17:44','',1,'http://t12pathshala.co.nf/2017/07/1-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(684,1,'2017-07-06 11:20:11','2017-07-06 11:20:11','<ol>\r\n 	<li><strong>Graffiti:</strong> Colo